text: This email and any attachments transmitted with it are confidential and/or legally privileged. It should not be used by anyone who is not the original intended recipient. If you have received this e-mail in error please inform the sender and delete it immediately from your mailbox or any other storage mechanism. Dhofar Insurance Company (S.A.O.G.) cannot accept liability for any statements made which are clearly the sender's own and not expressly made on behalf of Dhofar Insurance Company (S.A.O.G.) or one of its agents. Although the company has taken reasonable precautions to ensure that no viruses are present in this email, the company cannot accept responsibility for any loss or damage arising from the use of this email or attachments.

Si vous avez reçu cet e-mail par erreur, veuillez informer l'expéditeur et le supprimer immédiatement de votre boîte mail ou de tout autre mécanisme de stockage. Dhofar Insurance Company (S.A.O.G.) ne peut être tenue responsable des déclarations faites qui sont clairement celles de l'expéditeur et non exprimées au nom de Dhofar Insurance Company (S.A.O.G.) ou de l'un de ses agents.
